lead_paragraph: Kashima Antlers eventually succumbed to Real Madrid in the Club World Cup final on Sunday but gave the European champions a real scare and sent a message that football in Japan is on the rise.

headline.main: Kashima Show Japan on the Rise With Club World Cup Run
